        public static java.lang.String getCurrentFaceId(CruzrFaceCallBackImpl cruzrFaceCallBackImpl)
        获取当前表情Id
        Get the current expression Id
        Returns:
        若当前显示表情，则返回当前表情id；否则返回空字符串。
        If the expression is currently displayed, the current expression id is returned; otherwise, the empty string is returned.
